"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-06-18-Five-Olympic-Games-five-Olympic-Rings-mark-Gong-Lijiao-s-dream-1uwJhwqYUaQ-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Gong Lijiao of China competes in the women's shot put event at the Diamond League in Suzhou, east China's Zhejiang Province, April 27, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 242, \"end\": 247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999634134159433, \"rank\": 2.0087199672279713e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999211355515779, \"rank\": 7.885685840135083e-05, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suzhou\", \"score\": 0.9999999992519406, \"rank\": 7.481145073426015e-10, \"text\": \"Suzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suzhou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  China's veteran female shot putter Gong Lijiao will participate in her fifth edition of the Summer Olympics in Paris at the age of 35.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999634134159433, \"rank\": 2.0087199672279713e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 409, \"end\": 420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gong_Lijiao\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gong Lijiao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gong_Lijiao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gong_Lijiao\"}, {\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999852898328, \"rank\": 1.4710261485758332e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the world's most-decorated track and field athletes, Gong has won two world championships and one Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She threw 20.58 meters to establish her personal best and take home the gold from the pandemic-delayed Tokyo Olympics in 2021.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 738, \"end\": 752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999997116902, \"rank\": 2.882235127008815e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before that glorious moment, she finished in third, second and fourth place in the previous three editions of the Games in Beijing, London and Rio de Janeiro, respectivley.\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 885, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9966435989866771, \"rank\": 0.0033677043796922885, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9884145982221845, \"rank\": 0.01172090021379369, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 905, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999904782726, \"rank\": 9.52170918124243e-09, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite her victory in Tokyo, Gong never stopped trying to break new ground.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 959, \"end\": 964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9957445900073606, \"rank\": 0.004273587557419911, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I threw 20.53 meters, I knew that I would win the title,\\\" Gong told China Media Group (CMG).\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"score\": 0.9097771766187205, \"rank\": 0.09894162647973671, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After that, I felt such a relief and aimed for 21 meters.\\\"\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dieter Kollark of Germany became Gong's coach again ahead of this season's winter training session.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6001400150984415, \"rank\": 0.44835539676745884, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though the two did not meet immediately, Kollark made detailed training plans for Gong every day via the internet.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She began to increase her workload from June.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She has developed remarkable skills, flexibility, muscle energy and a peaceful mindset over a career spanning more than two decades.\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gong's top performance this season has been 19.72 meters, the seventh-best mark in the world, leaving her behind compatriot Song Jiayuan.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top-five shot putters have all surpassed 20 meters.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1762, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gong left for Germany to join coach Kollark this month, and will participate in a series of competitions as part of her pre-Olympic preparation.\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1777, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6001400150984415, \"rank\": 0.44835539676745884, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am at a different age, but I still have the same goal, which is, as always, to win the title and to surpass my best record,\\\" Gong said.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 2047, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": []}]}"